                        <Text fill="#e48d31" layoutX="14.0" layoutY="27.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="How do I add an Activity?" wrappingWidth="241.43505859375">
                           <font>
                              <Font size="20.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text layoutX="14.0" layoutY="52.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="To add an Activity (Something you need to do!) into the system simply click on the module that you wish to create the activity within, followed by clicking the Assignment that the activity will be associated with. You are then shown a list of task categories, pick the task that best aligns with the activity you are entering. From this screen here you can then click “Create New Activity” and simply fill in the boxes provided. The Activity will now appear also automatically on your Gantt Chart.TIP: Always include a Name and a Time length for your activity. " wrappingWidth="370.2060546875" />
