                              <Font size="20.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text layoutX="14.0" layoutY="59.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="On the same page as the “Create New Activity” button, on the right-hand side there is a second “Edit” button this button allows you to reopen the window that you created the Activity in. Select the activity you wish to change and press this “Edit Activity” Button. From here you can remove the current number of hours value and update it to represent the current level of work done." wrappingWidth="370.2060546875" />
