                           </font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text layoutX="14.0" layoutY="52.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Milestones are related to a number of set tasks. E.g. Reading, Writing, Creating, etc. Tasks can be put together to create a milestone, when you complete all the tasks you have put into a milestone it has been met. They can be used to create easy goals." wrappingWidth="370.2060546875" />
