                        <Text layoutX="14.0" layoutY="52.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="A requirement can be used to set an order that you wish to complete your tasks in. For example, if before you can write an essay you might need to research first. A requirement allows you to set this order, this can then be displayed on the Gantt Chart." wrappingWidth="375.6947956085205" />
